Eros International PLC A


            
            Eros International Plc provides integrated media and entertainment services. It engages in co-produce, acquire and distribute Indian language films in multiple formats worldwide including: theatrical, television syndication and digital platforms. The company was founded by Vijay Mohandas Ahuja and Arjan G. Lulla in 1977 and is headquartered in London, the United Kingdom.

            
            (See Full Profile)


  




